斯兄弟还与韩国流行男孩乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tomorrow-x-together">Tomorrow X Together</a> (TXT) 合作制作了一首名为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/txt-jonas-brother-do-it-like-that-3459307">“Do It Like That”</a>的全新单曲。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/joe-jonas-address-sophie-turner-split-onstage-jonas-brothers-concert-3495850">乔·乔纳斯 (Joe Jonas) 似乎在乔纳斯兄弟 (Jonas Brothers) 音乐会的舞台上对索菲·特纳 (Sophie Turner) 提出分手的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
